Company Description                    




                        The company formerly was Beijing Bus Co. Ltd.On January 3, 2008, the company replaced its 100% of the shares of the Beijing Bafangda passenger Transport Co.Ltd with the right to use the body of the Beijing public transportation buses over the next decade, after the reorganization ,the company's main business has been changed from the city bus passenger business to the car sales and business of transformation services and bus advertising. The main business scopes: design, production, agency, publish advertisements from domestic and foreign businesses; taxi passenger, inter-provincial road passenger, rail passenger transport; car rental; auto repair.                    


