                                                Beijing Bashi Media Co Ltd
                                             Company Snapshot
                                            









                                            
	Beijing Bashi Media Co Ltd operates in the New and used car dealers sector.
	
	In addition to historical fundamental analyses, the complete report available to purchase compares Beijing Bashi Media Co Ltd with three other
	automotive dealers and parts suppliers in Asia:
		
	Atlas Honda
	
		of Pakistan
		(2016
	sales of 55.02 billion Pakistan Rupees [US$522.16  million]
		of which 100%
		was Motorcycles),
	
	Fujian Zhangzhou Development Co Ltd
	
		(3.13 billion Chinese Renmimbi [US$465.96  million]
		of which 82%
		was Automobile Trade), and
	
	Deutsch Motors Incorporated
	
		which is
		
		based in South Korea
		(670.22 billion Korean Won [US$598.51  million]
		).
	
	Sales Analysis. 
	Beijing Bashi Media Co Ltd reported sales of 3.48 billion Chinese Renmimbi (US$517.97 million)
		for the
		
		year ending
		December of 2016.
	
		This
		
			represents
		
				an
			
			increase of 16.7%
		
		 versus 2015, when the company's sales were 2.99 billion Chinese Renmimbi.
	
		Sales of Car Wholesale&services saw an increase
		
			of
		20.0% in 2016, from
		2.51 billion Chinese Renmimbi to 3.02 billion Chinese Renmimbi.
		
			Not all segments of Beijing Bashi Media Co Ltd experienced an increase in sales in 2016:
			sales of Advertisement fell 6.7% to 476.60 million Chinese Renmimbi.
			

	




 


 
 


 
 


 
 











 



 













 










